rulesList.cssText: .chf-cta-icon-text { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
.chf-cta-icon-text { display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; padding: 12px; }
.chf-cta-icon-text__icon > svg, .chf-cta-icon-text__icon img { width: 24px; height: 24px; fill: currentcolor; display: block; }

.chf-cta-icon-text__notification { position: absolute; display: none; top: -5px; left: 9px; min-width: 16px; height: 16px; line-height: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px 4px; background-color: rgb(226, 0, 116); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }

.chf-cta-icon { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
.chf-cta-icon__notification { display: none; position: absolute; top: -5px; right: -4px; }

.chf-cta { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }

.chf-cta { display: inline-flex; cursor: pointer; height: 42px; padding: 0px 24px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 700; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgb(226, 0, 116); }
.chf-cta--combined { height: 40px; line-height: inherit; border-left: 0px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; }

.chf-divider { color: rgb(124, 124, 124); height: 1px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: currentcolor; margin: 0px 0px 24px; }
.chf-input-checkbox__inner { position: relative; display: flex; cursor: pointer; }

.chf-input-checkbox__inner::before { content: ""; display: block; flex-shrink: 0; width: 15px; height: 15px; border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 2px; margin-right: 6px; }

.chf-input-checkbox__inner::after { content: ""; display: none; position: absolute; left: 5px; top: 3px; width: 5px; height: 11px; transform: rotate(45deg); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(70, 168, 0); border-right: 1px solid rgb(70, 168, 0); }
.chf-input-text__input { width: 100%; height: 40px; color: rgb(107, 107, 107); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); border-radius: 4px; padding: 10px 12px; }
.chf-input-text--error .chf-input-text__input { border-color: rgb(217, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(252, 237, 237); color: rgb(217, 0, 0); }
.chf-input-text--dark .chf-input-text__input { color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); border-color: rgb(208, 208, 208); }
.chf-link-text { color: rgb(0, 115, 159); font-size: 15px; line-height: 18px; text-decoration: none; }
.chf-link { display: flex; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; }
.chf-link__icon svg, .chf-link__icon img { display: block; width: 24px; height: 24px; }
.chf-modal { font-family: TeleNeo, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box; }
.chf-modal input, .chf-modal optgroup, .chf-modal select, .chf-modal textarea { font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; appearance: none; }

.chf-modal { z-index: 10000; min-width: 320px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 18px; position: fixed; inset: 0px; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; }

.chf-modal__inner { position: relative; margin: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; padding: 48px 24px 24px; transform: translateY(100%); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.4s, transform 0.4s, -webkit-transform 0.4s; }

.chf-slide-item { display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: justify; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 800; padding: 24px 0px; margin-left: 16px; margin-right: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(140, 140, 140, 0.3); }
.chf-slide-item__text { display: flex; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; }

.chf-slide-item__arrow { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
.chf-slide-item__arrow { display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: end; justify-content: flex-end; -webkit-box-flex: 1; flex: 1 1 0%; }
.chf-tabs__header { font-size: 18px; line-height: 21px; font-weight: 800; -webkit-box-flex: 1; flex-grow: 1; text-align: center; }

.chf-tabs__item { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
.chf-tabs__item { display: block; height: 40px; padding: 0px 6px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(237, 237, 237); }
.chf-validation-errors { margin: 12px 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 700; display: none; }
.chf-bg-dark { position: fixed; inset: 0px; height: 100%; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); transition: opacity 0.4s; }
.chf-flex-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; -webkit-box-pack: justify; justify-content: space-between; margin-left: -24px !important; }

.chf-brandbar__wrap-item { display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; margin-left: auto; }

.chf-desktop-navigation__level-1 { position: relative; display: flex; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 800; white-space: nowrap; padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 40px; padding-bottom: 2px; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; min-height: 66px; max-height: 66px; }
.chf-desktop-navigation__level-1::after { display: none; content: ""; position: absolute; bottom: 0px; width: calc(100% - 56px); height: 4px; background: rgb(226, 0, 116); }
.chf-desktop-navigation__level-2 { display: block; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 26px; }

.chf-header.chf-header, .chf-header .chf-header__container, .chf-header .chf-header__inner, .chf-header .chf-header-logo img, .chf-header .chf-desktop-navigation__level-1, .chf-header .chf-meta-navigation__trigger, .chf-header .chf-header-flyout__close { transition: max-height 0.1s ease-out, min-height 0.1s ease-out; }

.chf-header-flyout__container { position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow-y: auto; max-height: calc(-64px + 100vh); z-index: 1; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 1px 2px inset; }

.chf-header-flyout__close { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }

.chf-header-flyout__close { position: absolute; top: 0px; right: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 1; min-height: 64px; max-height: 64px; }
.chf-header-logo img { width: auto; height: 64px; min-height: 64px; max-height: 64px; }
.chf-header { font-family: TeleNeo, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box; }
.chf-header input, .chf-header optgroup, .chf-header select, .chf-header textarea { font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; appearance: none; }
.chf-header__container { min-width: 320px; position: fixed; width: 100%; z-index: 2000; top: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 2px 9px; }
.chf-header__inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr; gap: 16px; max-width: 1604px; min-height: 64px; max-height: 64px; margin: 0px auto; }
.chf-header__wrap { display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; }
.chf-login__container { display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: reverse; flex-direction: column-reverse; max-width: 642px; margin: 0px auto; }

.chf-login__container { max-width: initial; -webkit-box-pack: justify; justify-content: space-between; -webkit-box-orient: horizontal; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: row; margin: 0px; }
.chf-login__top .p--tmd-heading-2 { font-size: 36px; line-height: 36px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
.chf-meta-navigation__trigger::after { display: none; content: ""; position: absolute; bottom: 0px; width: calc(100% - 24px); height: 4px; background: rgb(226, 0, 116); }
.chf-mobile-navigation__slide { position: absolute; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; left: 100%; width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: none; }

.chf-mobile-navigation__back { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }

.chf-navigation-bar__inner { display: flex; flex-wrap: nowrap; -webkit-box-pack: end; justify-content: flex-end; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; }
.chf-search-container { display: none; position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; left: 0px; top: 0px; z-index: 1; }
.chf-sidebar-linklist { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; max-width: 642px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
.chf-sidebar-linklist__headline { font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: rgb(226, 0, 116) !important; margin: 26px 0px !important; }
.nexus-pk-coin__gray-out { position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: 1; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.533); }
.nexus-pk-coin__form { max-width: 640px; margin: 12px auto; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; }
.nexus-pk-coin__form button { background-color: transparent; border: none; margin: 0px; }

.nexus-pk-coin__form button.nexus-pk-coin__record-button, .nexus-pk-coin__form button.nexus-pk-coin__record-button > span { display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; }
.nexus-pk-coin__form button.nexus-pk-coin__record-button.disabled > span > svg, .nexus-pk-coin__form button.nexus-pk-coin__record-button.recording > span > svg { fill: rgb(255, 255, 255); }

.nexus-pk-coin__form button.nexus-pk-coin__search-button { display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; padding: 0px 8px; position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 0px; height: 100%; }
.nexus-pk-coin__search-bar { border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); border-radius: 4px; margin: 0px; -webkit-box-flex: 1; flex: 1 1 0%; position: relative; }

.nexus-pk-coin__search-bar > input[type="text"] { font-family: TeleNeo; font-weight: 400; font-size: 18px; background-color: transparent; outline: none; padding: 6px; margin-right: 36px; width: calc(100% - 60px); min-width: 0px; height: 32px; border: 0px !important; }

.nexus-pk-coin__suggestions-container { background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 0px; margin: 0px; position: absolute; z-index: 1; top: 4px; width: 100%; }
.nexus-pk-coin__suggestions-container > li > a { cursor: pointer; display: block; padding: 6px 24px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; text-decoration: none; }
.nexus-pk-coin__suggestions-container > li > a:hover { background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237); text-decoration: underline; }
.nexus-pk-coin__suggestions-container > li.ass > a:active, .nexus-pk-coin__suggestions-container > li.ass > a:hover { color: inherit !important; text-decoration: none !important; }
.nexus-pk-coin__suggestions-container > li.sayt a { display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: start; justify-content: start; gap: 0.5em; }
.nexus-pk-coin__suggestions-container > li.sayt a img { height: 2em; width: 2em; object-fit: contain; }

.nexus-pk-coin__content-bg, .nexus-pk-coin__mobile-filter, .nexus-pk-coin__record-content { font-family: TeleNeo; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 100%; position: absolute; }
.nexus-pk-coin__exit-modal-wrapper { display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; position: fixed; inset: 0px; z-index: 2001; }
.nexus-pk-coin__exit-modal { font-family: TeleNeo; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px; width: 60%; max-width: 50em; }

.nexus-pk-coin__exit-modal > .buttons > button { cursor: pointer; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(226, 0, 116); border: none; border-radius: 4px; padding: 9px 24px; display: flex; gap: 6px; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; }
.nexus-pk-coin__exit-modal > .buttons > .cancel { color: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); }

.nexus-pk-coin__mobile-filter-foot > button { font-family: TeleNeo; font-weight: 700; font-size: inherit; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-block; padding: 9px; border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); border-radius: 4px; margin: 24px; }
.nexus-pk-coin__tools-footer, .nexus-pk-coin__tools-header { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 18px; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 18px; }
.nexus-pk-coin__tools-footer a, .nexus-pk-coin__tools-header a { font-weight: 700; white-space: nowrap; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
.nexus-pk-coin__tools-footer { margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: justify; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.nexus-pk-coin__tools-header-right { grid-column: 2 / 4; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: justify; justify-content: space-between; }
.nexus-pk-coin__tools-footer > .toggle > svg, .nexus-pk-coin__tools-header-right-1 > .toggle > svg { transform: rotate(180deg); width: 12px; height: 8px; }
.nexus-pk-coin__tools-views > label { cursor: pointer; padding: 4px 11px; border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); margin: 0px 0px 0px -1px; }
.nexus-pk-coin__tools-views > label > svg { fill: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 18px !important; height: 18px !important; vertical-align: middle !important; }
.nexus-pk-coin__filter { position: relative; white-space: nowrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); }

.nexus-pk-coin__filter > span { color: inherit; display: block; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 48px 6px 12px; position: relative; cursor: pointer; }

.nexus-pk-coin__filter > span > span.icon { width: 24px; height: 24px; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; position: absolute; top: 15px; right: 12px; }
.nexus-pk-coin__filter > span > span.icon > svg { fill: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 18px; }

.nexus-pk-coin__filter > ul { background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); list-style: none; border: 1px solid rgb(107, 107, 107); border-radius: 4px; padding: 0px; margin: 3px 0px 0px; width: 100%; display: none; position: absolute; left: 0px; z-index: 3; }

.chf-cta { appearance: none; text-transform: none; overflow: visible; font-family: inherit; font-size: 100%; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; background: none; border: 0px; padding: 0px; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }

.chf-cta { display: inline-flex; cursor: pointer; height: 42px; padding: 0px 24px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: 700; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgb(226, 0, 116); }
.chf-cta--combined { height: 40px; line-height: inherit; border-left: 0px; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; }

.chf-divider { color: rgb(124, 124, 124); height: 1px; border-width: 1px 0px 0px; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: initial; border-left-style: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: initial; border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: currentcolor; margin: 0px 0px 24px; }

rulesList.cssText: .esx-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr); gap: 12px; max-width: 1512px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 12px; }
.esx-grid--100 { display: block; max-width: 3800px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(242, 245, 255); }
.esx-grid--category { display: grid; grid-template-columns: [side-start] repeat(4, 1fr) [side-end main-start] repeat(8, 1fr) [main-end]; }
.esx-grid--guide { display: grid; grid-template-columns: [side-start] repeat(3, 1fr) [side-end main-start] repeat(8, 1fr) [main-end] 1fr; }
.esx-grid--hub { display: grid; grid-template-columns: [side-start] repeat(4, 1fr) [side-end main-start] repeat(8, 1fr) [main-end]; }
.esx-grid--simple-page .simple-page-item:not(:has(.l-outer--full-width-element)) { display: grid; grid-template-columns: [main-start] repeat(6, 1fr) [main-end]; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 12px; }

.esx-swiper-button-prev, .swiper-button-next { position: absolute; top: 50%; width: calc(var(--swiper-navigation-size)/44*27); height: var(--swiper-navigation-size); margin-top: calc(0px - var(--swiper-navigation-size)/2); z-index: 10; cursor: pointer; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--swiper-navigation-color, var(--swiper-theme-color)); }

.esx-swiper-button-prev::after, .swiper-button-next::after { font-family: swiper-icons; font-size: var(--swiper-navigation-size); letter-spacing: 0px; font-variant: initial; line-height: 1; text-transform: none !important; }
.swiper-pagination { position: absolute; text-align: center; transition: opacity 300ms; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); z-index: 10; }

.swiper-pagination-bullet { width: var(--swiper-pagination-bullet-width, var(--swiper-pagination-bullet-size, 6px)); height: var(--swiper-pagination-bullet-height, var(--swiper-pagination-bullet-size, 6px)); display: inline-block; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--swiper-pagination-bullet-inactive-color, #000); opacity: var(--swiper-pagination-bullet-inactive-opacity, 0.2); }
button.swiper-pagination-bullet { border: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-shadow: none; appearance: none; }

.swiper-pagination-progressbar .swiper-pagination-progressbar-fill { background: var(--swiper-pagination-color, var(--swiper-theme-color)); position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; transform: scale(0); transform-origin: left top; }
.swiper { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; position: relative; overflow: hidden; list-style: none; padding: 0px 0px 24px; z-index: 1; }
.swiper-wrapper { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: 1; display: flex; transition-property: transform, -webkit-transform; box-sizing: content-box; }
.swiper-slide { flex-shrink: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; position: relative; transition-property: transform, -webkit-transform; }
.swiper-autoheight .swiper-wrapper { -webkit-box-align: start; align-items: flex-start; transition-property: transform, height, -webkit-transform; }

.swiper-3d .swiper-slide-shadow, .swiper-3d .swiper-slide-shadow-left, .swiper-3d .swiper-slide-shadow-right, .swiper-3d .swiper-slide-shadow-top, .swiper-3d .swiper-slide-shadow-bottom { position: absolute; left: 0px; top: 0px; width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 10; }

.esx-anchor-nav { display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: end; justify-content: flex-end; -webkit-box-align: start; align-items: flex-start; padding: 24px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248); margin-bottom: 24px; }
.esx-anchor-nav__trigger { position: relative; width: 100%; padding-right: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: inherit; }
.esx-anchor-nav__trigger svg { position: absolute; right: 0px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(-90deg); width: 20px; color: rgb(0, 115, 159); }
.esx-anchor-nav__index { display: none; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; margin-top: 12px; }
.esx-anchor-nav__index { display: block; margin-top: 0px; border-right: 2px solid rgb(208, 208, 208); padding-right: 12px; }

.esx-anchor-nav__link.esx-anchor-nav__link--active { border-color: rgb(226, 0, 116); font-weight: 700; width: 100%; padding-right: 12px; display: block; border-right-width: 2px; border-right-style: solid; }

.esx-anchor-nav__tab-nav .esx-anchor-nav__scroll-indicator-left, .esx-anchor-nav__tab-nav .esx-anchor-nav__scroll-indicator-right { background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); position: absolute; bottom: 0px; height: 100%; width: 24px; cursor: pointer; }

.esx-anchor-nav__tab-nav .esx-anchor-nav__index { display: block; margin-top: 0px; text-align: left; overflow-x: scroll; white-space: nowrap; width: 100%; scrollbar-width: none; padding-bottom: 4px; }
.esx-anchor-nav__tab-nav .esx-anchor-nav__link--active::after { content: ""; width: 100%; height: 2px; background: rgb(226, 0, 116); position: absolute; left: 0px; bottom: -4px; z-index: 2; }

.esx-ordered-list { display: flex; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; -webkit-box-direction: normal; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
